      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
        <ul>
          <li>Open an account at <a href="https://bx.in.th" target="_blank">BX.in.th</a></li>
          <li>Create an API key for your BX.in.th account under <code>BX.in.th -> My Account -> Generate API Key</code> Give the API Key access only to deposit addresses</li>
          <li>Install the Coinpay plugin for your eCommerce shopping cart system</li>
          <li>In your own eCommerce website admin, enter your <a href="https://bx.in.th" target="_blank">BX.in.th</a> API ID into the Coinpay plugin settings</li>
          <li>Done: You are now able to receive payments in all available crypto-currencies, and these will automatically be forwarded (less network fee)* to your <a href="https://bx.in.th" target="_blank">BX.in.th</a> exchange account.</li>
        </ul>
